{"tid":2035800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「拉攏淺藍我地就贏」用數據講事實！淺藍亦能轉黃！","createTime":"2020-05-26T06:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T06:15:56.000Z","uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42f0db85b4f21c5ed692d45f6179156cf7ea3f81","tid":2035800,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzOW3sL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzOW3sL.png&h=7ce16b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到很多人分享那篇「淺藍不能轉黃」的文章。我的天，舊年下半年信任警察的比例由五成跌到兩成，中間這三成人不算是「淺藍轉黃」還是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n討論問題要講定義，那篇文章描述的那些不能改變的人是深藍而不是淺藍，不要搞錯。我認同很多自以為面向藍絲的文宣是圍爐取暖，但這絕對絕對不等於淺藍是不能或不用爭取的。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭的民望過去一個月已從 20 點慢慢爬升到 30 點了，不就正正說明游離民意的存在和需要爭取嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f19991bc8e03ebdace4579fd9361c3658c3ebd9","tid":2035800,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要贏！不是要圍爐取暖！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8b005f50ae6b267e3ebb343b34266db69fcc8b","tid":2035800,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"Cctai 或成最大贏家"}]}